# Tata Motors Traceability Portal Deployment Guide

## 1. Prerequisites
- Node.js (v18+)
- MySQL Server (with root access)
- npm (Node Package Manager)

## 2. Setup Instructions
1. Import database using schema.sql
2. Set environment variables in .env
3. Run:
   npm install
   cd client && npm install && npm run build
4. Start the server:
   node server.js
   (or use pm2 for production)

5. Access the portal:
   http://<your-ip>:5000

## 3. Folder Structure
- server.js       - Backend API
- client/         - React frontend
- .env            - Database config
- schema.sql      - DB structure

## 4. Notes
- Keep port 5000 open
- Must use static IP in LAN
-FRONTENED WORK ON 3000
